events.name: 3rd Annual Chefs Galore - A Food Tasting Extravaganza
events.description:
3rd Annual Chefs Galore /n Chefs Galore brings together over 125 amateur and professional chefs preparing dishes that are sure to delight your taste buds and romance your palate. Join us on June 20th from 12-4pm at St. Philip AME Church located at 240 Candler Rd in Atlanta 30317.
 Event Highlights 

 UNLIMITED FOOD TASTING (no tasting tickets). 
 Music and entertainment 
 People's Choice food judging 
 Special seating for elderly and disabled patrons. 
 Fun event for the entire family!! 
 Event goes from 12 noon - 4pm 
 Event Prices 
 under 6 - free 
 7-12 yrs. old- $11.54 
 13 and up - $22.09 
 Seniors (65+) - $16.82 

 Supporting a Good Cause 
 * Event Proceeds support youth based initiatives including: Angel Tree, Toys for Tots and Back to School Sunday. 
 Door prizes include an APPLE WATCH!!! 

   Connect with Chefs Galore on Social Media 

 Twitter - @chefsgalore 
 Instagram - chefsgalore 
 FB - chefsgalore 


  Privacy Policy: St. Philip AME Church (SPC) takes photographs and/ or videos during Chefs Galore. By attending Chefs Galore, you are consenting to photographs and/or videos taken on site and displayed in print, a/v, social media and/or on the SPC website without compensation.
